Package: binaryRasters
Type: Package
Title: classifies multiple raster into binary rasters
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Elvis Tangwa
Maintainer: The package maintainer <tangwaek@gmail.com>
Description: This packages lets you classifies many rastersinto binary map.
    Those working with multispecies distribution models may find the package useful.
    The package also stacks binary maps and map a gggplot of better visualization. 
    Finally the calculates the average area covered occupied by all the species you
    your have modeled 
